description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps Aaron Rodgers Press Conference from yesterday. Peter Doughtery of the Green Bay Press-Gazette, explains why he thinks this will be Aaron Rodgers last season with the Packers. And Chris Simms calls in to explain why he's not happy with the New York Jets.
